Author: FickleKaleidoscope
Text: Medical professionals would take you seriously and if they don’t go try someone else. ED’s don’t only exist in the context of an underweight BMI... you certainly sound like you have one based on your post. Try to find something enjoyable in your life and remember that people do care about you even if you don’t know it   *hugs*
